<h1>About Us</h1>
<p>Have you ever wanted to create your own group of like minded moms and build your own MamaTribe. Social Mama uses over 12 dimensions to match you with like-minded mothers in your local area.</p>
<p>Essentially, it is mom-dating. Whether you are looking to ask a questions, meet a friend, or collaborate on a business idea, Social Mama will match you with whom you 
are looking for. It is a simple as creating a profile and then viewing all your matches.</p>
